Hello Jessica,

I wanted to check in regarding your support ticket 00436889. We haven’t 
heard from you in a while, and I just wanted to see if you still need 
assistance with this issue.

If you’re still experiencing problems or have any updates to share, please 
let me know. If the issue has been resolved, I can go ahead and close the 
ticket on my end.

Please feel free to reply to this email with any updates or questions. 
We’re here to help you get the most out of your Netwrix products.

Ticket Number: 00436889
Ticket Subject: Entities Cannot Be Exported Due to Potential Low Disk Space 
(from Huawei)
Ticket Details: Dear Sir/Madam,

I submit this ticket on behalf of Huawei.

Currently, entities such as users and computers cannot be exported. There is 
no response after the Export button is clicked. The prompt shows the 
potential reason of this problem is low space disks. Please refer to the 
attached screenshots.

Until Feb 15, the system runs well.

Please help Huawei solve this problem. Thanks a lot in advance. (I prefer 
Adrian handle this ticket. He is always in charge of Huawei's case).

Thank you!

Adrian Draghici
Technical Support Team Lead
